---
title: Easy Creamy Mustard Chicken & Mash with Steamed Greens
description: Get ready for the ultimate comfort food with a gourmet twist! On the menu tonight we’ve got tender, golden-seared chicken smothered in a luscious, tangy mustard sauce, served over buttery mashed potatoes. On the side, perfectly steamed greens add a fresh, a vibrant touch.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67ca4c1e25f33d23e0b3dbc2-47cd6241-61b12745.jpeg
